These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: radish, kale, apple, artichoke
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, reading, rock-climbing, photography
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, disaster, drama, fantasy
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, soul, disco, jazz
4 different pets are kept: frog, rabbit, fish, ferret
 1. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person eating kale##1
 2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
 3. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the fan of soul##1
 4. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
 5. the fan of r&b is the person eating radish##1
 6. the fan of soul is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 7. the fan of disco is on the right of the person eating radish##1
 8. the person eating apple is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 9. the person watching drama movies is the person eating radish##1
10. the owner of the fish is the person watching disaster movies##1
11. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Food          | kale    | apple      | radish  | artichoke     |
| Hobby         | photography    | rock-climbing   | sudoku | reading      |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster       | thriller | drama     | fantasy    |
| Music-Genre   | jazz | soul         | r&b  | disco    |
| Pet           | fish      | ferret       | frog | rabbit |

