.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, tea, water, iced-tea
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, crime, epic, romance
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, salsa, country, techno
4 different pets are kept: mouse, guinea-pig, lizard, frog
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, rowing, sailing, lacrosse
 1. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
 2. the fan of punk is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
 4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
 5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
 6. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person drinking water##1
 7. the fan of techno is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
 8. the owner of the guinea-pig is the fan of techno##1
 9. the person watching epic movies is the fan of country##1
10. the fan of punk is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking water is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |       4       |
| Beverage      | tea      | almond-milk     | water    | iced-tea |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | crime   | epic   | romance           |
| Music-Genre   | salsa  | techno     | country    | punk         |
| Pet           | frog         | guinea-pig | lizard     | mouse        |
| Sport         | soccer     | lacrosse  | rowing | sailing       |

