.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-3::.
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, nectarine, onion, cherry
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, nigerian, argentine, german
4 different pets are kept: turtle, dog, hedgehog, hamster
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, biathlon, soccer, volleyball
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, jet-ski, bus, helicopter
 1. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
 3. the person eating onion is the owner of the hamster##1
 4. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
 5. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
 6. the person driving the helicopter is the person eating onion##1
 7. the argentine is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 8. the person driving the car is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
 9. the german is the owner of the dog##1
10. the nigerian is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
11. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
12. the person eating onion is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3    |       4       |
| Food          | raspberry    | cherry      | onion  | nectarine   |
| Nationality   | german     | argentine      | nigerian | pakistani      |
| Pet           | dog       | turtle         | hamster  | hedgehog         |
| Sport         | baseball | biathlon | soccer  | volleyball |
| Transport     | bus       | car         | helicopter   | jet-ski        |

