.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, juice, tea, mirinda
There 4 different types of food: carrot, pomegranate, watermelon, mango
There are 4 different nationalities: british, canadian, australian, brazilian
4 different pets are kept: mouse, fish, hedgehog, lizard
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, airplane, ship, car
 1. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
 2. the person eating mango is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
 3. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far right##1
 5. the person driving the scooter is on the far left##1
 6. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
 7. the brazilian is on the far right##1
 8. the person eating mango is on the right of the australian##1
 9. the canadian is on the left of the person eating carrot##1
10. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking tea is on the far left##1
12. the person driving the car is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | tea   | mirinda   | juice      | almond-milk     |
| Food          | watermelon     | carrot   | mango | pomegranate |
| Nationality   | canadian | australian | british   | brazilian       |
| Pet           | fish       | mouse      | lizard     | hedgehog |
| Transport     | scooter    | ship     | car     | airplane     |

