.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-5::.
There 4 different types of food: peas, banana, corn, cherry
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, woodworking, magic-tricks, puzzles
The people have 4 different jobs:  writer, pilot, entrepreneur, firefighter
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, italian, pakistani, british
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, frog, guinea-pig, chinchilla
 1. the writer is the owner of the chinchilla##1
 2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left##1
 3. the italian is on the far right##1
 4. the owner of the frog is the person eating corn##1
 5. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person eating banana##1
 6. the entrepreneur is on the far right##1
 7. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 8. the owner of the chinchilla is the writer##1
 9. the person eating cherry is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
10. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
11. the russian is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
12. the pilot is on the far left##1
13. the russian is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
14. the pakistani is on the right of the british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Food          | peas       | banana     | corn     | cherry  |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks  | puzzles | hiking | woodworking  |
| Job           | pilot | writer    | firefighter    | entrepreneur |
| Nationality   | british    | pakistani   | russian | italian |
| Pet           | goldfish       | chinchilla     | frog     | guinea-pig   |

