 1. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the argentine##1
 2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 4. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
 5. the person watching action movies is on the left of the mexican##1
 6. the mexican is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 7. the person driving the taxi is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 8. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the mexican##1
 9. the italian is on the far right##1
10. the person who's sport is badminton is the person driving the jet-ski##1
11. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person watching superhero movies##1
12. the argentine is the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |      4      |
