.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, mirinda, iced-tea, sprite
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, photography, video-games, collecting
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, librarian, dancer, electrician
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, volleyball, surfing, handball
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, bike, scooter, quad-bike
 1. the accountant is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 2. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left##1
 3. the person driving the bus is the person who's sport is surfing##1
 4. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
 5. the accountant is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is the person driving the quad-bike##1
 7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person driving the bike##1
 8. the person drinking mirinda is the librarian##1
 9. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
10. the person who's sport is badminton is the person drinking 7up##1
11. the dancer is on the left of the librarian##1
12. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
13. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |      3       |       4       |
| Beverage    | 7up        | mirinda       | sprite         | iced-tea |
| Hobby       | photography       | magic-tricks | collecting      | video-games     |
