 7. the person who's sport is tennis is the person drinking milk##1
 8. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1
10. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
11. the person who's hobby is singing is the person drinking fanta##1
12. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far left##1

