 7. the social-worker is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
 8. the person driving the tram is on the right of the lawyer##1
 9. the person drinking 7up is the person driving the snowmobile##1
10. the person drinking sprite is the owner of the turtle##1
11. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
12. the person drinking cola is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2        |      3      |      4       |
| Beverage    | 7up     | juice  | sprite       | cola      |
| Hobby       | card-games    | video-games        | chess  | filmmaking      |
| Job         | lawyer  | social-worker | police-officer | pilot |
| Pet         | ferret | rat          | turtle         | guinea-pig      |
| Transport   | snowmobile     | tram     | airplane       | bike          |

