.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, milk, almond-milk, soy-milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, camping, cooking, gardening
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, scientific, animation, sports
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, canadian, pakistani, american
4 different pets are kept: hamster, rabbit, goat, guinea-pig
 1. the pakistani is on the far left##1
 2. the person drinking milk is the person watching sports movies##1
 3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 4. the american is on the left of the colombian##1
 5. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 6. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person drinking soy-milk##1
 7. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 8. the colombian is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 9. the owner of the rabbit is the person watching animation movies##1
10. the person watching animation movies is on the far left##1
11. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
12. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |      3       |    4     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk       | almond-milk      | milk      | tea    |
| Hobby         | gardening | cooking | camping | photography  |
| Movie-Genre   | animation    | scientific     | sports      | documentary |
| Nationality   | pakistani  | american     | colombian    | canadian  |
| Pet           | rabbit  | guinea-pig       | hamster          | goat      |

