.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-19::.
There 4 different types of food: cucumber, peach, pumpkin, apricot
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, gardening, collecting, writing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, thriller, spy, disaster
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, tennis, biathlon, soccer
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, scooter, roller, trike
 1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left##1
 2. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 3. the person driving the roller is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 4. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
 5. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
 6. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
 7. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
 8. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person eating cucumber##1
 9. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person eating peach##1
10. the person who's sport is soccer is the person eating pumpkin##1
11. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
12. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far right##1
13. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |      3      |       4       |
