| Hobby         | collecting     | puzzles    | writing | gardening |
| Movie-Genre   | family | spy  | thriller      | disaster       |
| Sport         | biathlon      | surfing | tennis     | soccer        |
| Transport     | roller   | trike     | boat  | scooter       |

