.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-20::.
There 4 different types of food: tomato, papaya, spinach, garlic
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, chess, traveling, drawing
The people have 4 different jobs:  software-developer, videographer, manager, analyst
4 different pets are kept: fish, turtle, horse, guinea-pig
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, jet-ski, bus, trike
 1. the analyst is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 2. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
 3. the analyst is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 4. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the software-developer##1
 5. the owner of the horse is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 6. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 7. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the videographer##1
 8. the software-developer is the person driving the airplane##1
 9. the person eating spinach is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
10. the person eating garlic is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
11. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
12. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the manager##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |       3        |      4      |
| Food        | papaya    | garlic        | tomato        | spinach      |
| Hobby       | traveling       | puzzles       | chess      | drawing |
| Job         | videographer | analyst | manager | software-developer      |
| Pet         | fish          | guinea-pig         | turtle           | horse    |
| Transport   | bus         | jet-ski       | trike     | airplane   |

 